					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p136202">Force Blank timing issue - SNES vs. higan</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=136202#p136202"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Nov 08, 2014 5:14 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
